{"tid":11864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次轉會事件，方丈可能已經得罪咗港共","createTime":"2016-11-29T12:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T13:20:51.000Z","uid":33003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec36a5fae4a1eeff6a11b1e3fca68d8498e31dd","tid":11864,"uid":33003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"自從立會選舉後，高登時事台就充斥一班五毛係到扮打手不停互屌，搞到成版都係內訌私怨post，破壞晒高登時事台原有嘅討論氣氛，再加係爆料post都有講，方丈交會員資料比警犬係家常便飯，港共其實基本上已經控制晒高登嘅輿論，已經將高登「滅聲」<br />\n<br />\n可惜人算不如天算，方丈無啦啦搞單咁嘅野，搞到一大班人轉會，港共之前用幾個月時間，花咁多人力物力財力去「滅聲」，而家一切都付諸流水，再加上呢到admin未必會好似方丈咁輕易交出會員資料（希望啦），港共本來一個好完美嘅監控／滅聲計劃咁就失敗而回<br />\n<br />\n你睇lihkg開咗無耐，出面已經有巴打開post話有五毛想乞hkg+個code入黎，連高登出名五毛雨狗都已過埋黎仲開埋post<br />\n<br />\n可想而知唔只方丈急，連港共都開始急，如果要搵人祭旗，方丈應該走唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20d22c84e468b7fad793aa4b7007746bd483b7e","tid":11864,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"今次你仲唔仆街林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1723fe83e889663073457d8b9dc87b00e3880ec6","tid":11864,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404c30fa9662c3a9c5f5ae50176ef9b21f170e86","tid":11864,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"其實係早洩暗黑兵法反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e94c003f1b1a3a3ed16fce158f47b21